{"version":1,"ops":[{"type":1,"author":{"id":"ebc6eb80bae3658c4cf1ce84c011363931c578d7"},"timestamp":1482338735,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDU6SXNzdWUxOTY5Nzk0NTQ=","github-url":"https://github.com/rurban/Cpanel-JSON-XS/issues/78","origin":"github"},"title":"inf and NaN may be generated with allow_bignum","message":"If bignum support is enabled, then `inf` and `NaN` may be generated:\n```\n$ perl -MMath::BigInt -MCpanel::JSON::XS -E 'say Cpanel::JSON::XS-\u003enew-\u003eallow_bignum-\u003eencode([Math::BigInt-\u003enew(\"NaN\")])' \n[NaN]\n```\nSame for \"-inf\" and \"+inf\". Explicitly setting `stringify_infnan(0)` does not help.","files":null}]}